Columns representing an album

字段摘要

          The id for the album Type: INTEGER

          A non human readable key calculated from the ALBUM, used for searching, sorting and grouping Type: TEXT

          The artist whose songs appear on this album Type: TEXT

          The year in which the earliest songs on this album were released.

          The year in which the latest songs on this album were released.
static String NUMBER_OF_SONGS
          The number of songs on this album Type: INTEGER
static String NUMBER_OF_SONGS_FOR_ARTIST
          This column is available when getting album info via artist, and indicates the number of songs on the album by the given artist.
